languages.text: The {g|f:215d9f42b7e6435e9ed77337156e0fc3}Expanded{/g} Servoskull Swarm can save an ally from fatal damage if they're inside its area. The ally restores {uip|Heal|8eddb7d7975c4228b50f2270fc9ebf17}% Wounds. After that, the Servoskull Swarm automatically uses {g|f:24766e84d93647f083d03c90b83f942b}Diminish{/g}, thus losing the {g|f:215d9f42b7e6435e9ed77337156e0fc3}Expanded{/g} status.

languages.text: Once per combat, the servo-skull swarm can save an ally. If that ally suffers lethal damage in a 4-cell radius around the servo-skull swarm, that ally regains <u>(servo-skull swarm's {g|Encyclopedia:WarhammerFellowship}FEL{/g} bonus / 3)</u>% of their {g|Encyclopedia:MaxWounds}maximum wounds{/g} and remains in combat. Then, the servo-skull swarm suffers <u>(100 − {g|Encyclopedia:CareerOverseerGlossary}Overseer{/g}'s {g|Encyclopedia:SkillMedicae}Medicae{/g} / 5)</u>% {g|Encyclopedia:ShockDamage}shock damage{/g}.
languages.original_text: Один раз за бой рой сервочерепов может спасти союзника. Получив смертельный урон в радиусе 4 клеток от роя, союзник немедленно восстанавливает <u>(бонус {g|Encyclopedia:WarhammerFellowship}ОБЩ{/g} роя сервочерепов / 3)</u>% от своего {g|Encyclopedia:MaxWounds}максимального здоровья{/g} и остается в строю. Рой сервочерепов получает <u>(100 − {g|Encyclopedia:SkillMedicae}Медицина{/g} {g|Encyclopedia:CareerOverseerGlossary}надзирателя{/g} / 5)</u>% {g|Encyclopedia:ShockDamage}электрического урона{/g}.
